result.title: Stuck in the same rating for 2 years
result.content: I have doing competitive programming for 2 years.I solved all the DIV 2B problems, and then, I have been solving the DIV 2C problems topicwise. Unfortunately, I have stuck between the 1300- 1500 level for the two years. I am feeling very discouraged. Can you guys please suggest me what am I doing wrong? How should I practice?
